// Toggle
// On/off toggle switch with three size variants (sm, md, lg).

FUNCTION handleToggle()
  Flips the internal checked state.
  Calls onChange with the new boolean value.

---

FUNCTION Toggle(props) -> ReactNode                                       EXPORT
  Renders a pill-shaped toggle switch.
  Size is controlled by the size prop, mapped to Tailwind dimensions.
  Shows a sliding circle indicator that moves left/right to reflect checked state.
  Calls handleToggle on click.
